We can create a new site by clicking on the plus button at the bottom left corner.

8
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:33.210
Almost immediately we will be asked to give our site a name for this course.

9
00:00:33.210 --> 00:00:35.880
I'm going to set the name to Udemy.

10
